    DeepLogic Models

    Version 3-4 Models

    Version 3-4 Models, are the initial uploaded DeepLogic Models on Poe, these models are still in development ,and is less efficient compared to Reasoning and Ultimate Models.

    Reasoning 2-5 Models

    Reasoning Models are the upgraded version of the initial upload. These Models are more professional and enhances visual presentation.

    Ultimate 1-2 Models

    The Ultimate Models are the best featured reasoning DeepLogic Models, including better enhancement of the prompts, of the Reasoning and Integrated Models.

    Integrated and X Models

    These Models are configured for personal use, these models can be customized, for Chat and Workflow, there are currently 5 existing Models in this type.

    Prompting

    Prompting: Start

    After testing various prompts, we identified the most effective structure for creating engaging ones. This foundation allows us to tailor prompts for different scenarios and achieve the best results.

    Prompting: Inspiration

    By reviewing different prompt types, including RAG and text-generation, we developed a solid understanding of effective prompting, enabling us to create more tailored and impactful prompts.

    Prompting: Revising

    Through repeated cycles of editing and testing, we fine-tuned the model, making adjustments after each iteration until it met our desired specifications and consistently delivered the expected results.

    Prompting: Upgrading

    We started by adding instructions to the prompt and then entered a cycle of testing, analyzing, and revising. With each iteration, we fine-tuned the wording and structure to improve clarity and performance, ensuring the model aligned with our goals.
